14:39.280 --> 14:42.720
And we worked very closely together

14:42.720 --> 14:45.200
throughout the whole pre-production and post-production.

14:46.180 --> 14:49.800
And Frank and I have worked together for many years, so it's not

14:49.800 --> 14:53.620
an uncomfortable thing at all. We think very much alike.

