17:47.620 --> 17:51.960
the same ones that have done Star Wars and Raiders of the Lost Art.

17:52.500 --> 17:54.200
We did the great Muppet Caper there also.

17:57.360 --> 17:59.800
Why was it shot over in England? Any particular reason?

18:00.540 --> 18:03.480
