Okay, one last question here on Dark Crystal.

21:23.960 --> 21:28.340
Because of all the work you did on developing the characters in the world, anything like that,

21:30.040 --> 21:31.960
do you think there might be

21:31.960 --> 21:34.940
another Dark Crystal movie somewhere in the future?

21:35.900 --> 21:39.560
Well the story itself is complete in itself

21:40.040 --> 21:44.040
and so it doesn't lend itself to Dark Crystal 2.

21:44.040 --> 21:46.520
I don't think there will be a sequel as such.

21:47.100 --> 21:49.880
We could have another story in this same world.

21:50.660 --> 21:55.520
But I think we're kind of waiting until after this film opens to see how we feel about that.

21:57.440 --> 21:58.560
Yeah, they really

21:59.740 --> 22:03.200
they've had several fantasy movies after the summer that

22:03.960 --> 22:07.040
none of them really seem to capture the genre.

22:07.300 --> 22:11.680
In fact I guess one of the last and best was The Wizard of Oz and that was quite a lot of it.

22:11.680 --> 22:15.460
So in that sense I really hope you're successful with that because

22:15.460 --> 22:18.100
I really enjoyed the fantasy stories.

22:18.760 --> 22:24.180
Yes, to us it was a wonderful challenge. It was something we had a great time doing.

22:25.600 --> 22:27.640
And whether or not we

22:27.640 --> 22:31.800
are or we will be successful at it is something I have no

22:31.800 --> 22:35.560
idea yet. We won't really know until this whole moment.

22:38.560 --> 22:41.440
Yeah, sort of a calculated gamble in that sense.

22:41.440 --> 22:42.140
Yeah.

